1. git clone;
2. cd directory;
3. npm install;
4. mongo db install (https://www.mongodb.com/);
5. Install and run plug-in "Allow-Control-Allow-Origin" ( for Chrome: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/allow-control-allow-origi/nlfbmbojpeacfghkpbjhddihlkkiljbi);
6. sudo mongod (on mac) (run mongodb)
7. node server.js (run server)
8. npm start; (run client)